
Bindle Binaries Linux Firewall
===========================

   Bindle Binaries Linux Firewall is a collection of scripts and files which aid
   in the management of projects. 


Contents
--------

   1. Disclaimer
   2. Software Requirements
   3. Tested Platforms
   4. Maintainers
   5. Community
   6. Source Code
   7. Package Maintence Notes


